snippet.title: Camper Van: Make it Home Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description: Now on Kickstarter, Camper Van: Make It Home takes the organizational relaxation of Unpacking and applies it to a cozy van. "You will embark on a journey of personal discovery while you decorate your van and create a space for all your belongings." http://kck.st/3Ml1bJc #indiegames #campervan #vanlife
